    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165620/extras/e1276e6702865d88ca69bc8d9fe4ae22.avif?t=1739647279\" width=600 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165620/extras/49d1fcd816f5818372b2912ee56aec4a.poster.avif?t=1739647279\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165620/extras/49d1fcd816f5818372b2912ee56aec4a.webm?t=1739647279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165620/extras/49d1fcd816f5818372b2912ee56aec4a.mp4?t=1739647279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你对我们的星球和浩瀚宇宙了解多少？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在是时候检验你的知识了！踏上一段充满趣味问答、震撼视觉效果和惊人发现的激动人心之旅吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是探索地球的奇观、揭开宇宙的奥秘，还是与家人和朋友一较高下，这款游戏都为你提供了无限的学习和娱乐机会。准备好展示你的实力，夺取终极问答冠军的称号了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165620/extras/d774651b0d6b4184ce03add75a910f21.avif?t=1739647279\" width=600 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165620/extras/dc55232b5fc7c1fa0dd9a185c8eadd39.poster.avif?t=1739647279\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165620/extras/dc55232b5fc7c1fa0dd9a185c8eadd39.webm?t=1739647279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165620/extras/dc55232b5fc7c1fa0dd9a185c8eadd39.mp4?t=1739647279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挑战自己，体验4种独特模式：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>观看与学习</strong> - 你更喜欢视觉学习吗？通过观看视频后的问题，测试你的记忆力！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战役模式</strong> - 探索地球的各个地区，完成精彩的章节，赢取应得的奖牌！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快速游戏</strong> - 选择难度，随时畅玩，享受你喜欢的主题问答！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>锦标赛模式</strong> - 想展示你的所学？与朋友或家人一同竞争，争夺问答大师的称号！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过2000道题目，考验你的知识！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持最多4人的本地多人模式！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4种丰富多样的游戏玩法！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quizpedia 提供你需要的所有信息！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精彩的教育视频！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引人注目的视觉效果！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索关于地球及浩瀚宇宙的新奇知识吧！</p>",
